OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781032284
OL,3,CGrowth to slow and unemployment to
OL,4,Cjump to two million, says CBI
OL,6,FUK economic growth is set to falter
OL,7,Fand unemployment will worsen as the
OL,8,Fconflict in the Middle East and rising
OL,9,Fenergy costs weigh on consumers and
OL,10,Ffirms, new forecasts have warned.
OL,12,FInfluential business group the
OL,13,FConfederation of British Industry
OL,14,F(CBI) warned that around 200,000 more
OL,15,FBritons are on track to become
OL,16,Funemployed in a gloomy outlook for the
OL,17,Fstate of the economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
