CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781032284
OL,3,CGrowth to slow and unemployment to
OL,4,Cjump to two million, says CBI
OL,6,FIts latest economic forecast predicted
OL,7,Fthat UK unemployment will rise to 5.5%
OL,8,Fthis year, which would represent
OL,9,Faround two million people.
OL,11,FThe unemployment rate was most
OL,12,Frecently reported at 5%, or around 1.8
OL,13,Fmillion people, by the Office for
OL,14,FNational Statistics.
OL,16,FEconomists from the CBI said the
OL,17,Fweakening labour market is linked to
OL,18,Freduced business investment in the
OL,19,Fface of higher cost inflation and
OL,20,Fconcerns over consumer spending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
