FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781032284
OL,3,CGrowth to slow and unemployment to
OL,4,Cjump to two million, says CBI
OL,6,FIt predicted that unemployment will
OL,7,Fthen reduce to around 5.3% for 2027.
OL,9,FIt came as the organisation downgraded
OL,10,Fits growth projections for the next
OL,11,Ftwo years.
OL,13,FForecasts predicted that UK gross
OL,14,Fdomestic product (GDP) will slow from
OL,15,F1.4% growth last year to 1.1% in 2026
OL,16,Fand then 0.9% in 2027.
OL,18,FPreviously, it had pointed towards
OL,19,Fgrowth of 1.3% this year and 1.5% in
OL,20,F2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781032284
OL,3,CGrowth to slow and unemployment to
OL,4,Cjump to two million, says CBI
OL,6,FThe downbeat outlook is largely caused
OL,7,Fby the impact of the conflict in the
OL,8,FMiddle East, which has caused
OL,9,Finflation to lift above forecasts and
OL,10,Fdampened sentiment.
OL,12,FHigher global energy prices, disrupted
OL,13,Fsupply chains, and increased
OL,14,Funcertainty for businesses and
OL,15,Fconsumers are all set to weigh on
OL,16,Fgrowth.
OL,18,FLouise Hellem, chief economist at the
OL,19,FCBI, said: "What's happening around
OL,20,Fthe world is compounding the UK's low-
OL,21,Fgrowth story.
OL,26,@{D@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
