OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781032284
OL,3,CGrowth to slow and unemployment to
OL,4,Cjump to two million, says CBI
OL,6,F"We saw weak momentum throughout 2025,
OL,7,Fbut if it weren't for the latest
OL,8,Fglobal shocks, we could be having a
OL,9,Fmuch more positive conversation about
OL,10,Fthe economy today.
OL,12,F"Last year it was tariffs and this
OL,13,Fyear it's the conflict in the Middle
OL,14,FEast."
OL,16,FThe projections also indicated that
OL,17,Finflation is likely to increase
OL,18,F"towards 4%" by the end of this year,
OL,19,Fas higher energy costs feed through to
OL,20,Ffirms and households.
