OL,3,CGrowth to slow and unemployment to
OL,4,Cjump to two million, says CBI
OL,6,FUK consumer prices index (CPI)
OL,7,Finflation was most recently recorded
OL,8,Fat 2.8% in April but is expected to
OL,9,Faccelerate in the coming months.
OL,11,FThe CBI said it expects the Bank of
OL,12,FEngland to maintain interest rates at
OL,13,Ftheir current level of 3.75% for the
OL,14,Frest of this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
